---
import ArrowIcon from './ArrowIcon.astro';
---

<section class="section" id="stories" style="background: var(--soft)">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <div class="kicker">Growth Stories</div>
      <h2>Clear decisions. Stronger outcomes.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="story-grid">
      <article class="story-card featured reveal">
        <figure class="story-media" style="margin:0" id="storyMedia">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552664730-d307ca884978?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80"
            alt="A leadership team working together in a modern office"
            loading="lazy"
            onerror="this.closest('.story-media').classList.add('img-failed')"
          />
        </figure>
        <div class="story-inner">
          <div class="kicker">Client Story · Manufacturing</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:1.5rem; margin-bottom:8px;">Aligning leadership, hiring, and structure for a family manufacturer.</h3>
          <p>A practical advisory engagement turned disconnected people challenges into a clear growth plan.</p>
          <div class="story-flow">
            <div><span>Challenge</span>Growth had outpaced structure.</div>
            <div><span>Solution</span>Clarified leadership needs and hiring priorities.</div>
            <div><span>Results</span>A stronger team with a clear path forward.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="story-card story-side reveal" data-d="1">
        <div class="kicker">Decision Framework</div>
        <h3 style="font-size:1.5rem;">From one urgent hire to a better leadership plan.</h3>
        <p>Executive search becomes far more valuable when it also reveals what the organization needs next — not just the seat you're filling today.</p>
        <a class="button button-secondary" href="#" style="align-self:flex-start; margin-top:12px;">Read Story <ArrowIcon size={15} /></a>
        <p class="story-note">Illustrative composite — replace with your real client growth stories.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
